    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "I'm more in favor of the discriminated type union, seems more clear to me.\r\n\r\nWith it we can also be more precise about the type for each widget (like making `getWidgetRenderState` as required in the \"`AutocompleteWidget`\" type so we can avoid using `!` everywhere in the widget itself).",
